** ''[[絕冬城之夜2:_西门之谜|絕冬城之夜2: 西门之谜]]'' (2009)
* ''[[巫师_(游戏)|巫師]]'' (2007)

== 获奖 ==
除了不计其数的游戏奖项，公司也获得了一系列商业相关的奖项:
* 盈利 100 – 加拿大成长最快的公司 2005 (排名 81)
* 2008年10月，BioWare获得Mediacorp Canada Inc评选的[[阿尔伯特最佳雇主|阿尔伯特最佳雇主]]. 由[[Calgary_Herald|Calgary Herald]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.canada.com/calgaryherald/story.html?id=02b19397-2fdf-4039-ba29-b93eaf908adb|title=Calgary Herald，"Alberta's top 40 places to work"，October 18，2008|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015185038/http://www.canada.com/calgaryherald/story.html?id=02b19397-2fdf-4039-ba29-b93eaf908adb|archivedate=2015-10-15|accessdate=2011-04-22}}</ref>和[[Edmonton_Journal|Edmonton Journal]]共同颁发。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/story.html?id=5bc8514a-b0eb-4538-bab4-a63f11f51a16|title=Edmonton Journal，"Alberta's best focus on attracting，keeping staff"，October 31，2008|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090205184601/http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/story.html?id=5bc8514a-b0eb-4538-bab4-a63f11f51a16|archivedate=2009-02-05|accessdate=2011-04-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eluta.ca/top-employer-bioware|title=Reasons for Selection，2009 Alberta's Top Employers competition|accessdate=2011-04-22|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716024316/http://www.eluta.ca/top-employer-bioware|dead-url=no}}</ref>

所有获奖信息可以到BioWare网站上查阅。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bioware.com/bioware_info/awards/ |title=BioWare: BioWare Corporate And Community Awards<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2011-04-22 |archive-date=2010-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101127184850/http://www.bioware.com/bioware_info/awards/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

* Spike TV's 2010 Video Game Awards: Studio Of The Year (2010)
* Hall of Fame induction (2010)<ref>USA Today</ref>

